## Generative Art

Part of [Genuary24](https://genuary.art) and can be [viewed in action](https://deadred.openmindmap.org?t=0&fhid=b0060c3057106347).

A Node-RED flow which generates art, the program becomes the art. The connections pass the messages that make the nodes perform their tasks. A change in the connections, a change in the art, a change in the program. The nodes become particles, the particles become the program.

## Recursion, Reflection and Rethinking

Blurring the lines between coding, art and industry triggers a rethinking of what is possible and why it has become possible.  Node-RED is popular amongst industrial IoT, upon reflection though, one sees the particles that direct the data of Industry. Rectangles become nodes, lines come wires, flows become art.

It is **not** recommended to run this flow in Node-RED, it will cause the Node-RED instance to freeze up - without warning. This should only be executed in the [deadred](https://deadred.openmindmap.org?t=0&fhid=b0060c3057106347) viewer.

For more details on flows and flow execution, see the [precursor](https://flowhub.org/f/a3f6aebd9bb877bc) to this flow.
